Pero kakaiba talaga.

00:30:10.310 --> 00:30:11.000
Ngayong buwan,

00:30:11.440 --> 00:30:12.680
ang Central Plains Sword Alliance
at Camellia Island

00:30:12.680 --> 00:30:13.740
parehong nagpadala ng mga sulat.

00:30:14.070 --> 00:30:14.640
Bakit?

00:30:15.330 --> 00:30:17.350
Sabi nila,
isang kakaibang meteorite ang bumagsak kamakailan.

00:30:17.350 --> 00:30:19.010
May mga sabi-sabi na ito ay isang senyales

00:30:19.030 --> 00:30:21.510
na si Yique Yinyang
ay babalik sa mundong ito.

00:30:21.510 --> 00:30:22.550
Bakit sobrang tense?

00:30:23.190 --> 00:30:24.390
Kailangan ba yun?

00:30:26.200 --> 00:30:27.070
Oo, oo.

00:30:27.350 --> 00:30:28.680
May kinalaman ito kay Yique Yinyang.

00:30:28.680 --> 00:30:29.880
Dapat tayong maging maingat.

00:30:37.070 --> 00:30:37.670
nga pala,

00:30:38.270 --> 00:30:39.960
ito ang sagot sa Camellia Island.

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:41.310
Natapos ko na itong isulat.

00:30:41.310 --> 00:30:43.590
Dalhin ito kaagad sa istasyon ng post ng bayan

00:30:43.590 --> 00:30:45.640
at ihatid ito
sa Central Plains Sword Alliance.

