Sa
paglitaw ng mga labi ng Jile Sect,

00:31:38.160 --> 00:31:38.960
ang jianghu

00:31:39.790 --> 00:31:40.790
ay nasa gulat,

00:31:41.240 --> 00:31:42.770
at lahat ay kinilabutan.

00:31:43.030 --> 00:31:44.000
Kung alam ng iba

00:31:45.510 --> 00:31:47.270
Mayroon din akong
mga gintong mata at marka sa noo,

00:31:47.270 --> 00:31:47.830
tapos Zhoudi Tower...

00:31:47.830 --> 00:31:49.160
Kahit na malaman ng mga tao,

00:31:50.110 --> 00:31:50.680
kikilos ako

00:31:50.680 --> 00:31:51.880
bilang Pinuno ng Zhoudi Tower

00:31:51.880 --> 00:31:52.680
at sabihin sa kanila:

