Si Yique Yinyang

00:31:55.000 --> 00:31:56.550
ipinanganak na likas na masama?

00:31:57.920 --> 00:31:59.720
Kung ang mga gintong mata at noo ay marka

00:31:59.720 --> 00:32:00.960
nasa mukha ko din,

00:32:02.070 --> 00:32:03.930
magiging masama rin ba ako nang hindi mapapatawad?

00:32:04.790 --> 00:32:05.240
mga mukha,

00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:06.570
mga bagay na ito

00:32:07.270 --> 00:32:08.870
huwag mong tukuyin kung sino ka.

